<doc id="369535" url="https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=369535" title="Roncq">
Roncq

Roncq commune in the Nord department in northern Pháp.

It is from the border with Bỉ.

It kết nghĩa với Todmorden in England, Delbrück in Đức, and Selinkegny in Mali.





